{"tid":180062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦失竊 選委會明寄道歉書 --（之後當無事）","createTime":"2017-03-30T16:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T12:24:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b1f6c5e05773c37b39377914b46821a178faf2","tid":180062,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"即時要聞  2017-03-30 22:41:15 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n日前選舉事務處儲有選民登記資料的手提電腦懷疑失竊，約380萬選民個人資料隨時被盜，處方表示今日起會發信知會所有地方選區選民，「以提高他們的警覺性和減低潛在的損害，並就事件對選民造成的不便和困擾衷心致歉」。處方指，約55萬名已提供電郵地址的選民會在今晚起收到有關電郵，明日起亦會分批將信件郵寄至其餘選民，該信件亦會上載至選舉事務處網站。<br />\n<br />\n處方指，已就事件致函各政府部門及不同界別機構，包括金融、保險、電訊、零售、地產代理、資訊科技界別等，呼籲有關機構「作出適當措施」，以保障機構及資料當事人的利益。<br />\n<br />\n選民可登入選民資料網上查閱系統（ <a href=\"http://www.voterinfo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterinfo.gov.hk&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=165a4578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.voterinfo.gov.hk</a> ）查閱登記狀況和最新登記資料，如就信件有任何疑問，或發現資料有不尋常的情況，可與選舉事務處聯絡（ reoenq@reo.gov.hk ）。"},{"pid":"bdc9984c9dc57b86f55b2612562f6c152de0dc08","tid":180062,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"成個選舉事務處摺埋收皮<br />\n事務處班垃圾死全家啦"},{"pid":"003aad955e18bdb309e4ecb03b77fe0e1c57f59d","tid":180062,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"又用納稅人錢走去寄信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班狗官就人工照出，責任唔使負。"},{"pid":"83d927b5805405f052c885f97e3120b966fcce36","tid":180062,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"仆街啦"},{"pid":"4c6f6a848852d5ea34f594dc2ed6968c8e20ec24","tid":180062,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">私隱專員公署：「四月記得準時出糧就得啦！」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc4d1cc7f034224d625acdbe4cf07c321f4964c","tid":180062,"uid":89198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母全香港都知啦，你仲走去寄380萬封信做乜柒"},{"pid":"73108d13a05fff3f2d91d44dfbcc9cb44e4ebb01","tid":180062,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"上左大陸啦 仲做咩大龍鳳"},{"pid":"fd8905b4334c64f6638df258b86d62dff1c49b6a","tid":180062,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"俾人借大耳lone你政府幫我還？"},{"pid":"f9e9264592497d09c9e66c72de9bb229637672b8","tid":180062,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"認真, 依家我地d地址, 電話, 身份證no. 全部比唔知乜人拎哂<br />\n一句唔好意思請見諒就算數??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟個問責制存在仲有無意義?"},{"pid":"a56db8a2f5ad8e87bdecf9406bacd00f8b9fd178","tid":180062,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"浪費紙張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba12864ff1e138ac15230285f84770a3848d507","tid":180062,"uid":14717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"出錯用公帑向市民道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e76f95f73642bd893f35e6d38318f760cac297","tid":180062,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"一句唔好意思咁就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要追究清楚，另外全個政府全面加強審視私隱保護措施"},{"pid":"4d8f13f3c783ab6cdcd8e1912f3b9b54e81c2436","tid":180062,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"出左事寄封信道歉就算數<br />\n咁要個政府黎做乜<br />\n執左佢啦<br />\n不如組成一個新既政府<br />\n用新既身份證號碼"},{"pid":"63bb748c963213fa3a65d64d85d83321200a49be","tid":180062,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"道歉有鳩用咩，比個解決方法黎啦。"},{"pid":"5a8afb99447a864129b690dbd50e2f2435d5e21e","tid":180062,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">私隱專員公署：「四月記得準時出糧就得啦！」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇出過聲？"},{"pid":"434ce1bb5d542d942f7ca34d842afcf96de5bbc5","tid":180062,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"2016年9月5日 <br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉點票工作仍在進行。政制及內地事務局長譚志源早上會晤記者時，提到昨晚有多個投票站出現人龍，其中太古城票站更到凌晨兩點半才完成投票工作，他對此「誠懇致以衷心歉意」，並向借出場地的團體及機構致歉。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，選管會須於3個月內提交報告及改善措施，特區政府會配合及認真跟進，另感謝選管會選舉事務處、政府部門及公務員同事工作。<br />\n<br />\n問到將軍澳尚德票站被指多了300票，譚志源指相信選管會3個月內提交的報告會詳細交代此事。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>半年都黎緊，又搏人唔記得 </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0718b4e4f2dc2db3cde3e1b60be62f2d74c968","tid":180062,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"寄信把撚咩 搵返啲電腦未呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6ee667e6b991a67ca46dbb42133f82ec444a64","tid":180062,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:40:41.000Z","msg":"做選管會職員on9<br />\n祝你地百病纏身"},{"pid":"17125d93e07090668a731602c7173409389d38d7","tid":180062,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8359471a229d08bd814af32c5cf594c2d1e029","tid":180062,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3629a50e21ee89351cd785f5afbe5c619b8